---
name    : detroit-rubygems
version : 0.1.0
title   : Detroit RubyGems
summary : RubyGems plugin for Detroit

description:
  RubyGems plugin for Detroit build system.
  This plugin builds a gem during the package
  phase and releases it to rubygems.org
  (or other gem source) during the release phase.

resources:
  home: http://detroit.github.com/
  code: http://github.com/detroit/detroit-rubygems
  mail: http://groups.google.com/groups/rubyworks-mailinglist

